data.description: Welcome to 423 Silent Bluff Drive in Summerville, SC! This exceptional 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath home offers a desirable floor plan, with the owner's suite conveniently located on the main level and two additional bedrooms, along with a spacious loft, upstairs.Step inside and prepare to be dazzled by the stunning kitchen, featuring granite countertops and a massive island perfect for meal preparation and entertaining. The modern and sleek design enhances the overall charm and functionality of this space.What sets this home apart from new construction is the remarkable upgrades the seller has added. Step outside and admire the fully fenced in yard offering privacy and a safe area for outdoor activities. Inside, notice the elegant touches like the revitalizedcabinet handles that enhance the overall aesthetic of the home. The upgraded kitchen faucet with bottle washer make meal preparation a breeze, while the updated lighting fixtures create a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout.  Additional features include garage door opener and gutters, offering convenience and peace of mind.   Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional home on Silent Bluff Drive. Schedule a showing today and seize the opportunity to make this your dream home!
